<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="figure/F3/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div>
<figcaption><p>Signal detection algorithm performance (AUC) classified by event. Error bars reflect AUC 95% confidence intervals. AUC, Area Under the Receiver Operating Characteristic curve.</p></figcaption></figure><p id="P11">The next two analyses focus on the EB05 and LR05 signal scores, as the commonly applied representatives of their associated class.</p></section><section id="S5"><h3 class="pmc_sec_title">Performance at fixed points</h3>
