<li id="R13">
<span class="label">13.</span><cite>Hochberg AM, Hauben M, Pearson RK, et al.  An evaluation of three signal-detection algorithms using a highly inclusive reference event database. Drug Saf. 2009;32(6):509–525. doi: 10.2165/00002018-200932060-00007.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.2165/00002018-200932060-00007" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19459718/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Drug%20Saf&amp;title=An%20evaluation%20of%20three%20signal-detection%20algorithms%20using%20a%20highly%20inclusive%20reference%20event%20database&amp;author=AM%20Hochberg&amp;author=M%20Hauben&amp;author=RK%20Pearson&amp;volume=32&amp;issue=6&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;pages=509-525&amp;pmid=19459718&amp;doi=10.2165/00002018-200932060-00007&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R14">
